<div class="row">
<div class="large-12 columns text-center show-for-large-up" data-magellan-destination="home" id="home">
	<div class="splash-baltimore">
		<div class="small-centered large-10 columns">
			<div class="overlay overlay-first">
				<h2>Baltimore’s Interactive Food Market</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="small-centered large-7 columns">
			<div class="overlay">
				<h3>October 2014  &#8226;  Location TBD</h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="small-centered large-5 columns">
			<div class="overlay">
				<h5 data-magellan-destination="discover">Bringing together Baltimore’s most creative chefs and food purveyors for a weekend pop-up market that also includes a full lineup of culinary workshops and demos.</h5>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="text-center esl hide-for-large-up">
	<%= image_tag("logo.png") %>
	<h2>BALTIMORE'S INTERACTIVE FOOD MARKET</h2>
	<h5>October 2014  &#8226;  Location TBD</h5>
	<p>Bringing together Baltimore’s most creative chefs and food purveyors for a weekend pop-up market that also includes a full lineup of culinary workshops and demos.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="small-centered large-11 columns" id="discover">
	<div class="large-4 columns text-center esl">
		<%= image_tag("eat.png") %>
		<h1>EAT</h1>
		<p>Local chefs and food vendors will serve up new dishes and fan favorites. Each chef will create one brand-new dish for the market.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="large-4 columns text-center esl">
		<%= image_tag("shop.png") %>
		<h1>SHOP</h1>
		<p>Discover and buy artisan food products from Baltimore food entrepreneurs. Good food is being made across the city and region - from snacks to spreads  - and we’re bringing it together in one tasty market.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="large-4 columns text-center esl">
		<%= image_tag("learn.png") %>
		<h1>LEARN</h1>
		<p>The demo and workshop stage is the place to learn skills, tricks and recipes from the experts: cocktail mixing, oyster shucking, molecular gastronomy, or knife skills - whether you’re a professional chef or just learning to boil water.</p>
	</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="large-12 columns text-center show-for-large-up">
	<div class="splash-sails">
		<div class="small-centered large-9 columns">
			<div class="overlay overlay-first">
				<h2>Put some wind in our sails</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="small-centered large-7 columns">
			<div class="overlay">
				<h3 data-magellan-destination="contact">Get involved with our RocketHub campaign</h3>
			</div>
		</div>
		<a href="http://www.rockethub.com/projects/45114-clipper-city-market" target="_blank" class="button">RocketHub</a>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="text-center esl hide-for-large-up">
	<%= image_tag("clipper.png") %>
	<h2>PUT SOME WIND IN OUR SAILS</h2>
	<h5>Get involved with our RocketHub campaign</h5>
	<a href="http://www.rockethub.com/projects/45114-clipper-city-market"  class="button">RocketHub</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="row">
<div class="large-push-1 large-5 columns text-center esl copy" id="contact">

	<%= image_tag("vendor.png") %>
	<h1>VENDORS</h1>
	<p>Want to know more about what we're doing, or get involved as a vendor or volunteer? We'd love to hear from you at <a href="mailto:clippercitymarket@gmail.com">clippercitymarket@gmail.com</a></p>
</div>
<div class="large-pull-1 large-4 columns text-center esl copy">
	<h1>SIGN UP</h1>
	<p>Sign up here and you’ll be first to know about new vendors and workshops.</p>
	<%= form_for(@subscriber) do |f| %>
		<%= f.label :name %>
		<%= f.text_field :name %>

		<%= f.label :email %>
		<%= f.text_field :email %>

		 <%= f.submit "Sign Up", class: "button" %>
	<% end %>
	</form>
</div>
</div>
